author: Sorabain

text:
It's an old fashioned first person dungeon crawling RPG, where you draw your own maps on the touch screen, make your own team out of a range of classes, develop these characters through skill points (put into abilities, stat boosters, passive effects, etc). A ye olde RPG in modern trappings. 
It's also hardcore and brutal in its difficulty if you're not constantly paying attention and being cautious. For all this, though, it's excellent. Plus, I think it made me about 40 times better at RPGs.
